      "message": "I tested the two endpoints for performance by uploading a 144MB log and curling it 10 times.\n\nThe results are in seconds\n\nserver.Get() (This one):\n2.812253\n3.044217\n3.269969\n3.322050\n3.445983\n3.450356\n3.632683\n3.635545\n4.624599\n4.904788\n\nfetcher/renderer:\n3.202007\n3.243374\n3.268037\n3.494634\n3.574223\n3.586072\n3.610375\n3.751684\n3.796055\n4.083352\n\nOn average they\u0027re approximately the same.",
